item.title: Isle of Man, Jersey and Guernsey sign deal with UK over post-Brexit trade - BBC News
item.description:
Isle of Man, Jersey and Guernsey sign deal with UK over post-Brexit trade  BBC News

Free trade between the United Kingdom and the British crown dependencies is set to continue after Brexit next year, the Manx government has confirmed.
